Program: Discovery
Title: Treating Thalassaemia
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx50
Last Broadcast Date: 03 June 1998
A report on the progress being made to treat thalassemia. At a meeting in London doctors and medical experts discuss the crippling effects of the blood disorder disease which causes anaemia. Also in the programme the future of Hi Fi and the observatory manned by 'snowmen'.